Cúbranse.

31
00:05:19,818 --> 00:05:20,652
Vamos.

32
00:05:36,043 --> 00:05:37,044
Señor, atrás.

33
00:05:58,315 --> 00:06:00,192
¡Alfred!

34
00:06:16,166 --> 00:06:17,000
Alfred.

35
00:06:22,881 --> 00:06:24,967
No lleven la espada en vano.

36
00:06:25,133 --> 00:06:26,301
¡Luchen!

37
